\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}1 cup granulated {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/sugar/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 sugar}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 tablespoon cornstarch\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/3 cup plus 1 tablespoon unsweetened Dutch-process {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cocoa-powder/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 cocoa powder}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/8 teaspoon salt\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 1/2 cups whole milk \
{\listtext	\'95	}4 large egg yolks\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup heavy cream\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 teaspoon pure {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/extracts/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 vanilla extract}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 ounces good-quality bittersweet or semisweet chocolate, chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}Lightly sweetened {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cream/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 whipped cream}}, to serve, if desired\
